| Color Use              | Color Name          | Hex Code  | Description                                                                                                            |
| ---------------------- | ------------------- | --------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 🖤 **Background**      | True Black          | `#0F0F0F` | Pure dark canvas (already used in your Rive setup). Use this for body/background.                                      |
| 🌫 **Secondary BG**    | Charcoal Gray       | `#1C1C1E` | Slightly lighter than black; ideal for cards, overlays, shadows.                                                       |
| ⚪ **Text Primary**     | Bone White          | `#E5E5E5` | Clean and modern for large headings or text. Easy to read on black.                                                    |
| 🔘 **Text Secondary**  | Dust Gray           | `#9A9A9A` | For body text or captions, creating hierarchy.                                                                         |
| 🧊 **Accent**          | Cyber Blue          | `#3FBFFF` | Reference from *Inception* poster — neon sci-fi tone. Use for buttons, hover effects.                                  |
| 🔥 **Alert Accent**    | Blood Orange        | `#F0544F` | Inspired by the “Rumbling” poster – fiery, aggressive call-to-actions.                                                 |
| 🪐 **Highlight Glow**  | Interstellar Purple | `#A78BFA` | For subtle glows or ring effects like in space/sci-fi scenes.                                                          |
| 🛸 **Tertiary Detail** | Acid Green          | `#84FF7C` | Reference from that galaxy hand-touch poster. Use *very sparingly* for UI interactions (progress bars, active states). |

